title: Food Icons Pack - semi-realistic cartoon style w/ transparent backgrounds
description: 67 versatile 2D food icons in semi-realistic cartoon style with transparent backgrounds, available in 1024x1024, 512x512, 256x256 and 128x128 resolutions. PNG Format Included.
longDescription:
Satisfy Your digital Appetite with Our Delectable Food Icon Pack!


Delight your users with a feast for their eyes! Our Food Icon Pack serves up a delicious assortment of 67 semi-realistic cartoon style food items, perfect for a wide range of applications and games. Each icon is crafted with a unique pseudo-3D effect, offering a tantalizing tilt rather than a flat, top-down view. This scrumptious selection is not only mouthwatering but also versatile, suitable for both 2D environments and projects looking for that extra dimension without full 3D models.


With 1024x1024, 512x512, 256x256 and 128x128 resolutions available, these icons are ready to be plated into your project with no additional seasoning needed. Their transparent backgrounds ensure they can be laid over any table setting – from vibrant game scenes to sleek app interfaces. The variety is as vast as a buffet, ranging from hearty baked goods to exquisite main courses, ensuring you'll find the perfect dish to complement your digital cuisine.


This semi-realistic cartoon style is our chef's special, offering just the right blend of whimsy and realism – ideal for game developers looking to serve a similar aesthetic. Our collection will not only add flavor to your project but will also seamlessly blend into your existing design, appealing to the diverse palates of your user base.
technicalDetails:
Features:


  • Broad Variety: 67 versatile 2D food icons covering a comprehensive range of designs.
  • Unique Visual Appeal: Semi-realistic cartoon style that stands out on any platform.
  • Mobile-Friendly: Optimized for performance on mobile devices with multiple resolutions tailored for various screen sizes and quick load times.
  • Versatile Use: Perfectly suited for a variety of games and applications, from mobile and desktop to web-based projects.
  • Multiple Resolutions: Assets are sharp and clear at all sizes, with versions available in 1024x1024, 512x512, 256x256, and 128x128 pixels, ensuring crisp visuals on both high and low-end devices.
  • Transparent Backgrounds: Ready-to-use assets with transparent backgrounds for seamless integration into any scene or interface.
  • Consistent Design: A uniform style ensures a cohesive visual experience across your game or app.
  • PNG Format included: High-quality, lossless PNG files ensure flawless visuals while being easily adaptable for different platforms and engine versions.
  • Broad Compatibility: Tested and confirmed for use in all major graphic applications and platforms, including mobile development.
